<p><span>2017</span><span>年至<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月，安旭生物研发费用中职工薪酬分别为<span>525.25</span>万元、<span>665.94</span>万元、<span>896.65</span>万元、<span>833.24</span>万元，占比分别为<span>66.76%</span>、<span>54.83%</span>、<span>55.38%</span>、<span>50.13%</span>；材料金额分别为<span>186.11%</span>、<span>228.28%</span>、<span>362.57%</span>、<span>362.59%</span>。</span></p>
