<p><span>艾隆科技所处行业需要一定的软硬件开发能力，产品具有较高附加值。然而，数据显示，艾隆科技销售费用和管理费用连续四年及一期均高于研发费用支出。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，艾隆科技研发费用分别为</span><span>1536.45</span><span>万元、</span><span>2016.24</span><span>万元、</span><span>2030.34</span><span>万元、</span><span>2324.97</span><span>万元和</span><span>1385.86</span><span>万元，研发费用率分别为</span><span>9.37%</span><span>、</span><span>10.28%</span><span>、</span><span>8.49%</span><span>、</span><span>7.98%</span><span>和</span><span>15.33%</span><span>；销售费用分别为</span><span>1921.94</span><span>万元、</span><span>2560.53</span><span>万元、</span><span>3530.97</span><span>万元、</span><span>4567.14</span><span>万元和</span><span>1891.06</span><span>万元，销售费用率分别为</span><span>11.72%</span><span>、</span><span>13.06%</span><span>、</span><span>14.76%</span><span>、</span><span>15.67%</span><span>和</span><span>20.92%</span><span>；管理费用分别为</span><span>2619.45</span><span>万元、</span><span>2591.60</span><span>万元、</span><span>3348.39</span><span>万元、</span><span>3412.10</span><span>万元和</span><span>1442.07</span><span>万元，管理费用率分别为</span><span>15.98%</span><span>、</span><span>13.22%</span><span>、</span><span>13.99%</span><span>、</span><span>11.71%</span><span>和</span><span>15.96%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>截至</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月末，艾隆科技拥有</span><span>4</span><span>家全资子公司、</span><span>4</span><span>家控股子公司。其中，</span><span>3</span><span>家子公司</span><span>2019</span><span>年亏损。</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，亏损子公司数量上升至</span><span>5</span><span>家。</span></p>
<p><span>事实上，艾隆科技的子公司并非仅面临亏损问题。</span><span>2019</span><span>年</span><span>11</span><span>月，艾隆科技子公司广州艾隆收到国家税务总局广州市税务局第三稽查局《税务处理决定书》，因</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月取得他方开具的增值税发票，并进行了认证抵扣，但相关发票在</span><span>2019</span><span>年度被税务部门认定为不合规发票，导致补税并交纳滞纳金</span><span>28854.32</span><span>元。</span></p>
<p><span>此外，艾隆科技湖南分公司员工还曾涉及行贿。据湖南省衡阳市中级人民法院公布的（</span><span>2019</span><span>）湘</span><span>04</span><span>刑终</span><span>70</span><span>号文书，艾隆科技湖南分公司涉湖南省肿瘤医院药学部主任杨立平受贿案。胡某红是苏州艾隆科技有限公司湖南分公司的负责人，前后送出</span><span>24</span><span>万元换取项目采用艾隆科技的设备。</span></p>
<p><span>另据</span><span>(2017)</span><span>苏</span><span>0591</span><span>执</span><span>1819</span><span>号法律文书，艾隆科技曾因未履行已经发生法律效力苏园劳仲案字（</span><span>2017</span><span>）第</span><span>51</span><span>号仲裁裁决书中所确定的义务，被苏州工业园区人民法院冻结、扣划公司银行存款人民币</span><span>6</span><span>万元，</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>5</span><span>月成为被执行人。</span></p>
<p><span>对上述问题，中国经济网记者发送邮件至艾隆科技董秘办，截至发稿未收到回复。</span></p>
<p><strong><span>冲刺科创板</span><span>面临实际控制人持股比例较低的风险</span></strong></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技前身为苏州艾隆科技有限公司，成立于</span><span>2006</span><span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月</span><span>20</span><span>日。</span><span>2012</span><span>年</span><span>4</span><span>月</span><span>18</span><span>日，有限公司整体变更为股份有限公司。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技专注于医疗物资的智能管理领域，目前主要为各级医疗服务机构提供医疗物资智能化管理整体解决方案，产品主要包括覆盖自动化药房、自动化病区、自动化物流三大板块的医疗物资智能管理设备及软件信息平台。该公司具体产品包括快速发药机、高速发药机、输液成品分拣机、智能存取机等。目前主要应用于药品、耗材及其他医疗物资的智能管理，主要应用场景为大中型医院、社区医院、医药供应链服务企业、城市中央药房、中药自动集中代煎中心等。</span></p>
<p><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>2</span><span>日，艾隆科技在上交所网站披露招股说明书，拟于上交所科创板上市，保荐机构为海通证券股份有限公司，审计机构为立信会计师事务所（特殊普通合伙），发行人律师为北京观韬中茂律师事务所，评估机构为北京天健兴业资产评估有限公司。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技选择的上市标准为《上海证券交易所科创板股票上市规则》第</span><span>2.1.2</span><span>条规定的“（一）预计市值不低于人民币</span><span>10</span><span>亿元，最近两年净利润均为正且累计净利润不低于人民币</span><span>5000</span><span>万元，或者预计市值不低于人民币</span><span>10</span><span>亿元，最近一年净利润为正且营业收入不低于人民币</span><span>1</span><span>亿元”。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技本次拟公开发行股票数量不超过</span><span>1930</span><span>万股，不低于发行后总股本的</span><span>25%</span><span>，发行后总股本不超过</span><span>7720</span><span>万股。该公司拟募集资金</span><span>4.77</span><span>亿元，其中</span><span>2.05</span><span>亿元拟用于建设药房自动化设备生产基地项目，</span><span>5180.28</span><span>万元拟用于建设研发中心项目，</span><span>6003.85</span><span>万元拟用于营销及售后一体化建设项目，</span><span>1.60</span><span>亿元拟用于补充流动资金。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="244" src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/f9b80d3cffc9470dacd3e638fa0cd366.gif" /></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技的控股股东、实际控制人为张银花。招股说明书显示，张银花直接持有艾隆科技</span><span>2305.50</span><span>万股股份，占艾隆科技股份总数的</span><span>39.82%</span><span>，担任艾隆科技的董事长、总经理，为单一最大股东，对艾隆科技的财务和经营政策拥有决定权，故张银花为艾隆科技的控股股东及实际控制人。</span></p>
<p><span>本次发行完毕后，预计实际控制人控制艾隆科技的股份比例将进一步下降。对此，该公司在招股说明书中也提示风险称，实际控制人持股比例相对较低，可能存在股东大会决策效率较低的风险，以及公司未来经营发展产生不确定性的风险。</span></p>
<p><span>张银花，女，</span><span>1964</span><span>年出生，中国国籍，无境外永久居留权。</span><span>1985</span><span>至</span><span>1993</span><span>年为张家港市第一人民医院护士，</span><span>1993</span><span>年至</span><span>1995</span><span>年任张家港市中医院护士，</span><span>1995</span><span>年至</span><span>2004</span><span>年任江苏省卫生医药有限公司副总经理，</span><span>2004</span><span>年</span><span>4</span><span>月至</span><span>2009</span><span>年</span><span>4</span><span>月任苏州市国征医药有限公司执行董事兼经理，</span><span>2006</span><span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月至</span><span>2010</span><span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月任艾隆有限监事，</span><span>2010</span><span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月至今任艾隆科技法定代表人、董事长兼总经理。</span></p>
<p><strong><span>创业板“改道”科创板</span><span>不到一年拟多募集</span><span>1.6</span><span>亿元</span></strong></p>
<p><span>值得一提的是，本次并非艾隆科技第一次冲击</span><span>IPO</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2019</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>19</span><span>日，苏州艾隆科技股份有限公司（以下简称“艾隆科技”）向证监会递交创业板上市申请。</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>2</span><span>日，艾隆科技再在上交所网站披露招股说明书，拟于上交所科创板上市，</span></p>
<p><span>不到一年时间内，艾隆科技即从创业板“转道”科创板。而改变的不止是上市地点，还有其募集资金金额。</span></p>
<p><span>中国经济网记者对比艾隆科技创业板招股说明书和科创板招股说明书后发现，本次科创板上市，该公司拟募集资金</span><span>4.77</span><span>亿元，较其创业板拟募集资金多</span><span>1.60</span><span>亿元。这</span><span>1.60</span><span>亿元该公司将全部用于补充流动资金，两版招股说明书中其它募投项目及投资额均一致。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技创业板招股说明书显示，该公司拟募集资金</span><span>3.17</span><span>亿元，其中</span><span>2.05</span><span>亿元拟用于建设药房自动化设备生产基地项目，</span><span>5180.28</span><span>万元拟用于建设研发中心项目，</span><span>6003.85</span><span>万元拟用于营销及售后一体化建设项目。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="139" src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/c09623f8249b4745ae47376b3d1ab468.gif" /></p>
<p align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span>来源：艾隆科技<span>2019</span>年<span>6</span>月<span>19</span>日报送的创业板招股说明书</span></p>
<p><span><strong>销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金连续四年不及营业收入</strong></span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，艾隆科技实现营业收入分别为</span><span>1.64</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.96</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.39</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.91</span><span>亿元和</span><span>9038.24</span><span>万元；实现净利润分别为</span><span>2117.89</span><span>万元、</span><span>4065.06</span><span>万元、</span><span>5205.05</span><span>万元、</span><span>5441.94</span><span>万元和</span><span>1054.51</span><span>万元；实现归属于母公司所有者的净利润分别为</span><span>2161.98</span><span>万元、</span><span>3987.62</span><span>万元、</span><span>5112.95</span><span>万元、</span><span>5355.52</span><span>万元和</span><span>1330.79</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="382" src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/05bb598e194347309c6dca1945f14c94.gif" /></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年至</span><span>2019</span><span>年，艾隆科技营业收入同比增幅分别为</span><span>19.60%</span><span>、</span><span>22.04%</span><span>和</span><span>21.81%</span><span>；净利润同比增幅分别为</span><span>91.94%</span><span>、</span><span>28.04%</span><span>和</span><span>4.55%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，艾隆科技经营活动产生的现金流量净额分别为</span><span>-1191.70</span><span>万元、</span><span>2181.70</span><span>万元、</span><span>4278.37</span><span>万元、</span><span>5429.89</span><span>万元和</span><span>1546.08</span><span>万元。其中，</span><span>2016</span><span>年至</span><span>2019</span><span>年，该公司经营活动产生的现金流量净额连续四年不及其净利润。</span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，艾隆科技销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金分别为</span><span>1.38</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.75</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.23</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.87</span><span>亿元和</span><span>1.27</span><span>亿元。</span><span>2016</span><span>年至</span><span>2019</span><span>年，该公司销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金连续四年不及同期营业收入。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技还在招股说明书中披露了其</span><span>2020</span><span>年前三季未经审计的财务数据。</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-9</span><span>月，艾隆科技预计实现营业收入为</span><span>1.56</span><span>亿元，同比增幅为</span><span>6.67%</span><span>；预计实现归属于母公司股东的净利润为</span><span>2800.00-3000.00</span><span>万元，同比增幅为</span><span>75.48%-88.02%</span><span>；预计实现归属于母公司股东的扣除非经常性损益的净利润</span><span>2100.00-2300.00</span><span>万元，同比增幅为</span><span>43.83%-57.53%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span><strong>负债总额过去两年半持续上涨</strong></span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，艾隆科技资产总额分别为</span><span>3.85</span><span>亿元、</span><span>4.33</span><span>亿元、</span><span>5.31</span><span>亿元、</span><span>5.98</span><span>亿元和</span><span>6.49</span><span>亿元，负债总额分别为</span><span>2.09</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.09</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.67</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.81</span><span>亿元和</span><span>2.50</span><span>亿元。</span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，艾隆科技流动资产分别为</span><span>1.49</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.90</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.79</span><span>亿元、</span><span>3.24</span><span>亿元和</span><span>3.58</span><span>亿元，占比分别为</span><span>38.60%</span><span>、</span><span>43.80%</span><span>、</span><span>52.46%</span><span>、</span><span>54.16%</span><span>和</span><span>55.17%</span><span>；非流动资产分别为</span><span>2.36</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.43</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.53</span><span>亿元、</span><span>2.74</span><span>亿元和</span><span>2.91</span><span>亿元，占比分别为</span><span>61.40%</span><span>、</span><span>56.20%</span><span>、</span><span>47.54%</span><span>、</span><span>45.84%</span><span>和</span><span>44.83%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>同期，艾隆科技货币资金余额分别为</span><span>3612.28</span><span>万元、</span><span>4550.75</span><span>万元、</span><span>7661.75</span><span>万元、</span><span>7045.57</span><span>万元和</span><span>7402.82</span><span>万元，占各期末流动资产的比重分别为</span><span>24.32%</span><span>、</span><span>24.00%</span><span>、</span><span>27.49%</span><span>、</span><span>21.75%</span><span>和</span><span>20.66%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，该公司流动负债余额分别为</span><span>1.36</span><span>亿元、</span><span>5701.59</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.63</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.48</span><span>亿元和</span><span>2.18</span><span>亿元，主要包括短期借款、应付票据、应付账款、应交税费等；非流动负债余额分别为</span><span>7315.70</span><span>万元、</span><span>5210.72</span><span>万元、</span><span>428.31</span><span>万元、</span><span>3221.22</span><span>万元和</span><span>3207.73</span><span>万元，主要为长期借款、预计负债，该公司非流动负债变化主要系长期借款金额变化所致。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年末、</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末和</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月末，艾隆科技短期借款金额分别为</span><span>5602.03</span><span>万元、</span><span>0</span><span>万元、</span><span>2789.61</span><span>万元、</span><span>2581.37</span><span>万元和</span><span>8582.68</span><span>万元，占流动负债的比例分别为</span><span>41.14%</span><span>、</span><span>0%</span><span>、</span><span>17.14%</span><span>、</span><span>17.40%</span><span>、</span><span>39.33%</span><span>；长期借款余额分别为</span><span>7000.00</span><span>万元、</span><span>5000.00</span><span>万元、</span><span>0.00</span><span>万元、</span><span>2805.00</span><span>万元和</span><span>2740.00</span><span>万元，占非流动负债的比例分别为</span><span>95.68%</span><span>、</span><span>95.96%</span><span>、</span><span>0%</span><span>、</span><span>87.08%</span><span>和</span><span>85.42%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，艾隆科技资产负债率（母公司）分别为</span><span>52.89%</span><span>、</span><span>24.27%</span><span>、</span><span>29.14%</span><span>、</span><span>27.44%</span><span>和</span><span>37.16%</span><span>；流动比率分别为</span><span>1.09</span><span>、</span><span>3.33</span><span>、</span><span>1.71</span><span>、</span><span>2.18</span><span>和</span><span>1.64</span><span>；速动比率分别为</span><span>0.87</span><span>、</span><span>2.77</span><span>、</span><span>1.45</span><span>、</span><span>1.83</span><span>和</span><span>1.37</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span><strong>超六成应收账款逾期</strong></span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>1-6</span><span>月，艾隆科技应收账款（含合同资产）余额分别为</span><span>6180.41</span><span>万元、</span><span>9977.75</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.46</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.87</span><span>亿元和</span><span>1.76</span><span>亿元，占营业收入比例分别为</span><span>37.70%</span><span>、</span><span>50.89%</span><span>、</span><span>60.97%</span><span>、</span><span>64.04%</span><span>、</span><span>97.39%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2019</span><span>年末应收账款余额较</span><span>2018</span><span>年末增长</span><span>4074.63</span><span>万元，</span><span>2018</span><span>年末应收账款余额较</span><span>2017</span><span>年末增长</span><span>4609.50</span><span>万元，</span><span>2017</span><span>年末应收账款余额较</span><span>2016</span><span>年末增长</span><span>3797.34</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，该公司坏账准备分别为</span><span>409.39</span><span>万元、</span><span>655.26</span><span>万元、</span><span>1012.43</span><span>万元、</span><span>1542.86</span><span>万元和</span><span>1751.03</span><span>万元；应收账款净额分别为</span><span>5771.02</span><span>万元、</span><span>9322.50</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.36</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.71</span><span>亿元和</span><span>1.59</span><span>亿元。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="290" src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/fe5ae837b5c64b6b88003b687c21eac0.gif" /></p>
<p><span>其中，该公司账龄</span><span>1</span><span>年以内应收账款余额分别为</span><span>5041.25</span><span>万元、</span><span>8731.62</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.11</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.39</span><span>亿元和</span><span>1.13</span><span>亿元，占比分别为</span><span>81.57%</span><span>、</span><span>87.51%</span><span>、</span><span>76.29%</span><span>、</span><span>74.69%</span><span>和</span><span>64.45%</span><span>；账龄</span><span>1</span><span>年以上应收账款余额分别为</span><span>1139.16</span><span>万元、</span><span>1246.13</span><span>万元、</span><span>3458.64</span><span>万元、</span><span>4723.77</span><span>万元和</span><span>6258.82</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>18.43%</span><span>、</span><span>12.50%</span><span>、</span><span>23.70%</span><span>、</span><span>25.31%</span><span>和</span><span>35.55%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>截至</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末、</span><span>2019</span><span>年末和</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月末，艾隆科技逾期应收账款余额分别为</span><span>3332.28</span><span>万元、</span><span>5898.19</span><span>万元、</span><span>9589.34</span><span>万元和</span><span>1.17</span><span>亿元，占比分别为</span><span>33.40%</span><span>、</span><span>40.43%</span><span>、</span><span>51.38%</span><span>和</span><span>66.54%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="123" src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/b42e8bb229754360bb1651e1ede0d8d0.gif" /></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技称，公司存在一定比例客户实际回款周期与信用期差异，主要系公司部分客户涉及项目以新建、扩建院区为主，该类医院受到财政预算审批限制等原因，项目付款周期较长，导致部分医院客户或经销商客户回款周期较长；部分客户资金紧张，未能及时安排付款。</span></p>
<p><span>招股说明书显示，同行业可比上市公司健麾信息</span><span>2016</span><span>年末、</span><span>2017</span><span>年末、</span><span>2018</span><span>年末和</span><span>2019</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月末健麾信息逾期应收账款占比分别为</span><span>57.66%</span><span>、</span><span>36.50%</span><span>、</span><span>34.84%</span><span>和</span><span>53.64%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>截止</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>9</span><span>月</span><span>21</span><span>日，报告期各期末，艾隆科技的应收账款回款比例分别为</span><span>85.27%</span><span>、</span><span>73.67%</span><span>、</span><span>40.56%</span><span>、</span><span>14.81%</span><span>，期后回款比例较低。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="158" src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/3a2c5f23f7a94da59b909ece571eb8d9.gif" /></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，艾隆科技应收账款周转率分别为</span><span>3.22</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年、</span><span>2.43</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年、</span><span>1.95</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年、</span><span>1.75</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年和</span><span>1.00</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，同行业可比上司公司应收账款周转率平均值分别为</span><span>8.94</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年、</span><span>6.38</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年、</span><span>6.28</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年和</span><span>6.78</span><span>次</span><span>/</span><span>年。</span></p>
<p><span><strong>毛利率高于同业</strong></span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，艾隆科技主营业务毛利率分别为</span><span>51.47%</span><span>、</span><span>55.04%</span><span>、</span><span>60.09%</span><span>、</span><span>57.25%</span><span>和</span><span>60.29%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>据了解，艾隆科技主营业务收入包括自动化药房系列产品、自动化病区系列产品、自动化物流系列产品、维保及技术服务以及其他产品。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，该公司自动化药房板块实现营业收入分别为</span><span>1.29</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.43</span><span>亿元、</span><span>1.60</span><span>亿元和</span><span>5278.62</span><span>万元，占主营业务收入的比例分别为</span><span>67.81%</span><span>、</span><span>61.69%</span><span>、</span><span>56.73%</span><span>和</span><span>61.86%</span><span>；自动化病区板块实现营业收入分别为</span><span>2736.41</span><span>万元、</span><span>2984.65</span><span>万元、</span><span>2216.58</span><span>万元和</span><span>848.20</span><span>万元，占主营业务收入的比例分别为</span><span>14.44%</span><span>、</span><span>12.91%</span><span>、</span><span>7.85%</span><span>和</span><span>9.94%</span><span>；自动化物流板块实现营业收入分别为</span><span>1218.54</span><span>万元、</span><span>3219.76</span><span>万元、</span><span>6762.02</span><span>万元和</span><span>959.03</span><span>万元，占主营业务收入的比例分别为</span><span>6.43%</span><span>、</span><span>13.93%</span><span>、</span><span>23.95%</span><span>和</span><span>11.24%</span><span>；维保及技术服务费实现营业收入分别为</span><span>1403.47</span><span>万元、</span><span>1853.92</span><span>万元、</span><span>2470.25</span><span>万元和</span><span>1332.67</span><span>万元，占主营业务收入的比例分别为</span><span>7.41%</span><span>、</span><span>8.02%</span><span>、</span><span>8.75%</span><span>和</span><span>15.62%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>过去三年及一期，艾隆科技自动化药房系列产品毛利率分别为</span><span>62.74%</span><span>、</span><span>66.87%</span><span>、</span><span>68.95%</span><span>、</span><span>68.71%</span><span>；自动化病区系列产品毛利率分别为</span><span>32.30%</span><span>、</span><span>60.68%</span><span>、</span><span>48.96%</span><span>、</span><span>51.74%</span><span>；自动化物流系列产品毛利率分别为</span><span>55.74%</span><span>、</span><span>42.28%</span><span>、</span><span>44.91%</span><span>和</span><span>54.63%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技表示，公司自动化药房系列主要产品毛利率总体呈上升趋势。主要系公司在产品价格保持稳定的基础上，改进生产工艺，降低生产成本所致。</span><span>2017</span><span>年度，智能分包机主要为公司为满足客户整体解决方案的需求外购的产品。</span><span>2018</span><span>年度开始，公司部分智能分包机通过</span><span>OEM</span><span>模式进行生产，生产成本比直接对外采购成品要低，平均成本有所下降。自动化物流系列产品毛利率有所波动，主要因为产品结构变动所致。</span></p>
<p><span>过去三年及一期，和佳医疗、健麾信息和海尔生物</span><span>3</span><span>家同行业可比上市公司主营业务毛利率平均值分别为</span><span>56.59%</span><span>、</span><span>55.53%</span><span>、</span><span>51.56%</span><span>和</span><span>51.85%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>对于公司主营业务毛利率总体高于同行业可比上市公司平均水平，艾隆科技表示，与其他可比公众公司毛利率存在一定差异，主要原因是公司所处细分行业和具体产品与其他公司存在差异所致。</span></p>
<p><span><strong>过去四年及一期研发费用率波动</strong></span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，艾隆科技研发费用分别为</span><span>1536.45</span><span>万元、</span><span>2016.24</span><span>万元、</span><span>2030.34</span><span>万元、</span><span>2324.97</span><span>万元和</span><span>1385.86</span><span>万元，占营业收入的比例分别为</span><span>9.37%</span><span>、</span><span>10.28%</span><span>、</span><span>8.49%</span><span>、</span><span>7.98%</span><span>和</span><span>15.33%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="150" src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/3cf6ece976a34a9f8cd75f81b045ce88.gif" /></p>
<p><span>据中国经济网记者了解，该公司研发费用的增长主要系研发人员薪酬增加所致。该公司研发及设计人员从</span><span>2017</span><span>年底的</span><span>71</span><span>人增至</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月的</span><span>117</span><span>人，职工薪酬、研发领料消耗随之提高。</span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，艾隆科技研发费用中，职工薪酬分别为</span><span>550.24</span><span>万元、</span><span>822.27</span><span>万元、</span><span>1122.87</span><span>万元、</span><span>1,214.78</span><span>万元和</span><span>801.09</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>35.81%</span><span>、</span><span>40.78%</span><span>、</span><span>55.30%</span><span>、</span><span>52.25%</span><span>和</span><span>57.80%</span><span>；材料费分别为</span><span>118.32</span><span>万元、</span><span>219.43</span><span>万元、</span><span>310.47</span><span>万元、</span><span>560.65</span><span>万元和</span><span>317.85</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>7.70%</span><span>、</span><span>10.88%</span><span>、</span><span>15.29%</span><span>、</span><span>24.11%</span><span>和</span><span>22.93%</span><span>；折旧及摊销分别为</span><span>461.93</span><span>万元、</span><span>277.84</span><span>万元、</span><span>205.93</span><span>万元、</span><span>132.87</span><span>万元和</span><span>79.01</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>30.06%</span><span>、</span><span>13.78%</span><span>、</span><span>10.14%</span><span>、</span><span>5.71%</span><span>和</span><span>5.70%</span><span>；差旅费分别为</span><span>35.72</span><span>万元、</span><span>112.65</span><span>万元、</span><span>108.53</span><span>万元、</span><span>166.36</span><span>万元和</span><span>69.26</span><span>万元你，占比分别为</span><span>2.33%</span><span>、</span><span>5.59%</span><span>、</span><span>5.35%</span><span>、</span><span>7.16%</span><span>和</span><span>5.00%</span><span>；技术服务费分别为</span><span>266.75%</span><span>、</span><span>476.01</span><span>万元、</span><span>235.74</span><span>万元、</span><span>201.03</span><span>万元和</span><span>82.25</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>17.36%</span><span>、</span><span>23.61%</span><span>、</span><span>11.61%</span><span>、</span><span>8.65%</span><span>和</span><span>5.93%</span><span>；设计费分别为</span><span>69.00</span><span>万元、</span><span>94.34</span><span>万元、</span><span>19.57</span><span>万元、</span><span>0</span><span>万元和</span><span>0</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>4.49%</span><span>、</span><span>4.68%</span><span>、</span><span>0.96%</span><span>、</span><span>0%</span><span>和</span><span>0%</span><span>；办公费分别为</span><span>26.53</span><span>万元、</span><span>8.06</span><span>万元、</span><span>8.78</span><span>万元、</span><span>10.61</span><span>万元和</span><span>6.52</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>1.73%</span><span>、</span><span>0.40%</span><span>、</span><span>0.43%</span><span>、</span><span>0.46%</span><span>和</span><span>0.47%</span><span>；其他费用分别为</span><span>7.96</span><span>万元、</span><span>5.65</span><span>万元、</span><span>18.45</span><span>万元、</span><span>38.67</span><span>万元和</span><span>29.87</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>0.52%</span><span>、</span><span>0.28%</span><span>、</span><span>0.91%</span><span>、</span><span>1.66%</span><span>和</span><span>2.16%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="289" src="//p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/8db299f145c24ee4a8cdc9322ceb6113.gif" /></p>
<p><span>过去三年及一期，同行业可比上市公司研发费用率平均值分别为</span><span>8.36%</span><span>、</span><span>7.33%</span><span>、</span><span>8.47%</span><span>和</span><span>7.65%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>招股说明书显示，截至</span><span>2019</span><span>年末，艾隆科技及子公司已取得</span><span>56</span><span>项软件着作权和</span><span>387</span><span>项专利，其中发明专利</span><span>151</span><span>项（</span><span>PCT</span><span>国际发明专利</span><span>1</span><span>项），研发人员</span><span>106</span><span>人；同行业可比上市公司和佳医疗已取得</span><span>135</span><span>项软件着作权和</span><span>103</span><span>项专利，研发人员</span><span>206</span><span>人；海尔生物已取得</span><span>22</span><span>项软件着作权和</span><span>229</span><span>项专利，研发人员</span><span>277</span><span>人。截至</span><span>2019</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>30</span><span>日，同行业可比上市公司健麾信息已取得</span><span>52</span><span>项软件着作权和</span><span>81</span><span>项专利，研发人员</span><span>65</span><span>人。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="243" src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/cce098a04bcb484588b15d8d4b0053cf.gif" /></p>
<p><span>不过，从最近一年研发投入来看，艾隆科技仍不敌和佳医疗和海尔生物。</span><span>2019</span><span>年，艾隆科技研发费用为</span><span>2324.97</span><span>万元，研发费用率为</span><span>7.98%</span><span>；和佳医疗研发费用为</span><span>6033.55</span><span>万元，研发费用率为</span><span>4.95%</span><span>；海尔生物研发费用为</span><span>1.21</span><span>亿元，研发费用率为</span><span>11.99%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><strong><span>销售费用率较同行业公司平均值高逾</span><span>8</span><span>个百分点</span></strong></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技所处行业需要一定的软硬件开发能力，产品具有较高附加值。而中国经济网查阅招股说明书后发现，过去四年及一期，艾隆科技销售费用和管理费用均高于研发费用支出。</span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，艾隆科技销售费用分别为</span><span>1921.94</span><span>万元、</span><span>2560.53</span><span>万元、</span><span>3530.97</span><span>万元、</span><span>4567.14</span><span>万元和</span><span>1891.06</span><span>万元，销售费用率分别为</span><span>11.72%</span><span>、</span><span>13.06%</span><span>、</span><span>14.76%</span><span>、</span><span>15.67%</span><span>和</span><span>20.92%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，同行业可比上市公司销售费用率平均值分别为</span><span>15.41%</span><span>、</span><span>13.70%</span><span>、</span><span>12.96%</span><span>和</span><span>12.44%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技销售费用主要由工薪支出、差旅费、业务招待费、售后服务费、会务咨询费构成，过去四年及一期，五项费用合计占销售费用的比例超过</span><span>75%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，艾隆科技研发费用中，职工薪酬分别为</span><span>683.71</span><span>万元、</span><span>886.36</span><span>万元、</span><span>1303.74</span><span>万元、</span><span>1632.15</span><span>万元和</span><span>900.28</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>35.57%</span><span>、</span><span>34.62%</span><span>、</span><span>36.92%</span><span>、</span><span>35.74%</span><span>和</span><span>47.61%</span><span>；差旅费分别为</span><span>446.47</span><span>万元、</span><span>565.45</span><span>万元、</span><span>704.70</span><span>万元、</span><span>877.40</span><span>万元和</span><span>194.32</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>23.23%</span><span>、</span><span>22.08%</span><span>、</span><span>19.96%</span><span>、</span><span>19.21%</span><span>和</span><span>10.28%</span><span>；业务招待费分别为</span><span>183.34</span><span>万元、</span><span>192.77</span><span>万元、</span><span>435.23</span><span>万元、</span><span>668.23</span><span>万元和</span><span>214.40</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>9.54%</span><span>、</span><span>7.53%</span><span>、</span><span>12.33%</span><span>、</span><span>14.63%</span><span>和</span><span>11.34%</span><span>；会务咨询费分别为</span><span>29.74</span><span>万元、</span><span>155.50</span><span>万元、</span><span>161.09</span><span>万元、</span><span>168.68</span><span>万元和</span><span>3.15</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>1.55%</span><span>、</span><span>6.07%</span><span>、</span><span>4.56%</span><span>、</span><span>3.69%</span><span>和</span><span>0.17%</span><span>；展览宣传费分别为</span><span>29.52</span><span>万元、</span><span>87.62</span><span>万元、</span><span>141.70</span><span>万元、</span><span>191.00</span><span>万元和</span><span>22.42</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>1.54%</span><span>、</span><span>3.42%</span><span>、</span><span>4.01%</span><span>、</span><span>4.18%</span><span>和</span><span>1.19%</span><span>；售后服务费分别为</span><span>166.59</span><span>万元、</span><span>175.99</span><span>万元、</span><span>259.10</span><span>万元、</span><span>387.28</span><span>万元和</span><span>278.78</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>8.67%</span><span>、</span><span>6.87%</span><span>、</span><span>7.34%</span><span>、</span><span>8.48%</span><span>和</span><span>14.74%</span><span>；运输费分别为</span><span>75.80</span><span>万元、</span><span>90.16</span><span>万元、</span><span>128.29</span><span>万元、</span><span>196.40</span><span>万元和</span><span>86.47</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>3.94%</span><span>、</span><span>3.52%</span><span>、</span><span>3.63%</span><span>、</span><span>4.30%</span><span>和</span><span>4.57%</span><span>；折旧摊销费分别为</span><span>127.43</span><span>万元、</span><span>146.47</span><span>万元、</span><span>148.90</span><span>万元、</span><span>135.11</span><span>万元和</span><span>42.25</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>6.63%</span><span>、</span><span>5.72%</span><span>、</span><span>4.22%</span><span>、</span><span>2.96%</span><span>和</span><span>2.23%</span><span>；车辆使用费分别为</span><span>60.49</span><span>万元、</span><span>50.19</span><span>万元、</span><span>52.52</span><span>万元、</span><span>59.92</span><span>万元和</span><span>15.34</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>3.15%</span><span>、</span><span>1.96%</span><span>、</span><span>1.49%</span><span>、</span><span>1.31%</span><span>和</span><span>0.81%</span><span>；办公费分别为</span><span>66.54</span><span>万元、</span><span>63.89</span><span>万元、</span><span>73.90</span><span>万元、</span><span>78.97</span><span>万元和</span><span>27.12</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>3.46%</span><span>、</span><span>2.50%</span><span>、</span><span>2.09%</span><span>、</span><span>1.73%</span><span>和</span><span>1.43%</span><span>；招标费分别为</span><span>9.53</span><span>万元、</span><span>55.44</span><span>万元、</span><span>73.93</span><span>万元、</span><span>74.67</span><span>万元和</span><span>38.83</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>0.50%</span><span>、</span><span>2.17%</span><span>、</span><span>2.09%</span><span>、</span><span>1.63%</span><span>和</span><span>2.05%</span><span>；其他费用分别为</span><span>42.77</span><span>万元、</span><span>90.69</span><span>万元、</span><span>47.87</span><span>万元、</span><span>97.34</span><span>万元和</span><span>67.70</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>2.23%</span><span>、</span><span>3.54%</span><span>、</span><span>1.36%</span><span>、</span><span>2.13%</span><span>和</span><span>3.58%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="314" src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/e282aff295804102badfc8f669b7542c.gif" /></p>
<p><span><strong>管理费用率高于同业</strong></span></p>
<p><span>2016</span><span>年、</span><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，艾隆科技管理费用分别为</span><span>2619.45</span><span>万元、</span><span>2591.60</span><span>万元、</span><span>3348.39</span><span>万元、</span><span>3412.10</span><span>万元和</span><span>1442.07</span><span>万元，管理费用率分别为</span><span>15.98%</span><span>、</span><span>13.22%</span><span>、</span><span>13.99%</span><span>、</span><span>11.71%</span><span>和</span><span>15.96%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年、</span><span>2018</span><span>年、</span><span>2019</span><span>年和</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，同行业可比上市公司管理费用率平均值分别为</span><span>9.59%</span><span>、</span><span>8.30%</span><span>、</span><span>7.88%</span><span>和</span><span>7.41%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技解释称，公司管理费用率与可比公司平均水平相比较高，主要因为与和佳医疗、海尔生物相比，公司收入规模相对较小，规模效应尚不明显，随着公司收入规模的增长，管理费用率整体下降。</span></p>
<p><span>过去四年及一期，艾隆科技研发费用中，职工薪酬分别为</span><span>614.67</span><span>万元、</span><span>880.48</span><span>万元、</span><span>1263.48</span><span>万元、</span><span>1421.75</span><span>万元和</span><span>527.67</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>23.47%</span><span>、</span><span>33.97%</span><span>、</span><span>37.73%</span><span>、</span><span>41.67%</span><span>和</span><span>36.59%</span><span>；折旧摊销费分别为</span><span>468.47</span><span>万元、</span><span>642.40</span><span>万元、</span><span>829.96</span><span>万元、</span><span>833.78</span><span>万元和</span><span>460.53</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>17.88%</span><span>、</span><span>24.79%</span><span>、</span><span>24.79%</span><span>、</span><span>24.44%</span><span>和</span><span>31.94%</span><span>；中介服务费分别为</span><span>305.25</span><span>万元、</span><span>264.48</span><span>万元、</span><span>214.03</span><span>万元、</span><span>208.85</span><span>万元和</span><span>43.40</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>11.65%</span><span>、</span><span>10.21%</span><span>、</span><span>6.39%</span><span>、</span><span>6.12%</span><span>和</span><span>3.01%</span><span>；办公费分别为</span><span>183.80</span><span>万元、</span><span>197.57</span><span>万元、</span><span>244.69</span><span>万元、</span><span>227.84</span><span>万元和</span><span>109.39</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>7.02%</span><span>、</span><span>7.62%</span><span>、</span><span>7.31%</span><span>、</span><span>6.68%</span><span>和</span><span>7.59%</span><span>；租赁及水电费分别为</span><span>273.78</span><span>万元、</span><span>211.09</span><span>万元、</span><span>283.94</span><span>万元、</span><span>211.37</span><span>万元和</span><span>91.92</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>10.45%</span><span>、</span><span>8.14%</span><span>、</span><span>8.48%</span><span>、</span><span>6.19%</span><span>和</span><span>6.37%</span><span>；招待费分别为</span><span>168.43</span><span>万元、</span><span>174.43</span><span>万元、</span><span>186.61</span><span>万元、</span><span>156.19</span><span>万元和</span><span>66.28</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>6.43%</span><span>、</span><span>6.73%</span><span>、</span><span>5.57%</span><span>、</span><span>4.58%</span><span>和</span><span>4.60%</span><span>；差旅费分别为</span><span>85.83</span><span>万元、</span><span>100.21</span><span>万元、</span><span>156.57</span><span>万元、</span><span>208.37</span><span>万元和</span><span>63.95</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>3.28%</span><span>、</span><span>3.87%</span><span>、</span><span>4.68%</span><span>、</span><span>6.11%</span><span>和</span><span>4.43%</span><span>；其他费用分别为</span><span>131.49</span><span>万元、</span><span>120.94</span><span>万元、</span><span>169.12</span><span>万元、</span><span>143.96</span><span>万元和</span><span>78.94</span><span>万元，占比分别为</span><span>5.02%</span><span>、</span><span>4.67%</span><span>、</span><span>5.05%</span><span>、</span><span>4.22%</span><span>和</span><span>5.47%</span><span>。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="383" src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201102/e80821a017b44caea62da27b3ee50029.gif" /></p>
<p><strong><span>8</span><span>家子公司</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年</span><span>5</span><span>家亏损</span></strong></p>
<p><span>截至</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月末，艾隆科技拥有</span><span>4</span><span>家全资子公司、</span><span>4</span><span>家控股子公司。</span></p>
<p><span>2019</span><span>年，子公司苏州艾隆信息技术有限公司（以下简称“艾隆信息”）亏损</span><span>82.92</span><span>万元、广州艾隆医疗科技有限公司（以下简称“广州艾隆”）亏损</span><span>22.05</span><span>万元，苏州医橙网医疗科技有限公司（以下简称“医橙网”）亏损</span><span>184.47</span><span>万元，若上述子公司不能及时扭亏为盈，会影响艾隆科技的整体经营业绩。</span></p>
<p><span>广州艾隆成立于</span><span>2012</span><span>年</span><span>10</span><span>月</span><span>12</span><span>日，注册资本</span><span>500</span><span>万元。</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，广州艾隆延续亏损，当期亏损额</span><span>86.05</span><span>万元，去年同期，其亏损</span><span>22.05</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>医橙网成立于</span><span>2015</span><span>年</span><span>9</span><span>月</span><span>6</span><span>日，注册资本</span><span>1000</span><span>万元。</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，广州艾隆延续亏损，当期亏损额</span><span>100.55</span><span>万元，去年同期，其亏损</span><span>184.47</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆信息成立于</span><span>2014</span><span>年</span><span>7</span><span>月</span><span>14</span><span>日，注册资本</span><span>500</span><span>万元，实收资本</span><span>300</span><span>万元。</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年，艾隆信息延续亏损，当期亏损额</span><span>267.32</span><span>万元，去年同期，其亏损</span><span>82.92</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>除上诉三家子公司外，艾隆科技子公司苏州艾洁医疗科技有限公司</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年亏损</span><span>68.84</span><span>万元，去年同期，其亏损</span><span>22.26</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>艾隆科技子公司苏州优点优唯医疗科技有限公司</span><span>2020</span><span>年上半年亏损</span><span>170.03</span><span>万元，去年同期其净利润</span><span>369.84</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span><strong>分公司营销涉及行贿</strong></span></p>
<p><span>据中国裁判文书网</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>14</span><span>日公布的</span><span>(2017)</span><span>苏</span><span>0591</span><span>执</span><span>1819</span><span>号法律文书显示，艾隆科技曾因未履行已经发生法律效力苏园劳仲案字（</span><span>2017</span><span>）第</span><span>51</span><span>号仲裁裁决书中所确定的义务，被苏州工业园区人民法院冻结、扣划公司银行存款人民币</span><span>6</span><span>万元，</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>5</span><span>月成为被执行人。</span></p>
<p><span>另据湖南省衡阳市中级人民法院公布的（</span><span>2019</span><span>）湘</span><span>04</span><span>刑终</span><span>70</span><span>号文书，艾隆科技涉湖南省肿瘤医院药学部主任杨立平受贿案。</span></p>
<p><span>胡某红是艾隆科技湖南分公司的负责人。</span><span>2013</span><span>年上半年胡某红通徐某特介绍与杨立平相识。湖南省肿瘤医院对药房进行智能化改造时胡某红多次向杨立平推荐公司生产的设备并请杨立平给予关照。杨立平根据徐某特、胡某红提供的设备参数设计了智能化药房项目的招标条件。最终省肿瘤医院智能化药房项目中的部分标段使用胡某红公司提供的设备。</span></p>
<p><span>2013</span><span>年下半年，在智能化药房项目完工后胡某红向杨立平推荐了用于医院药品输送的轨道物流项目。杨立平在院务会上积极推荐该项目，最终省肿瘤医院通过该项目胡某红以湖南艾丁格尔科技有限公司（朋友朱星宪的公司）的名义与省肿瘤医院签订购买服务协议。</span></p>
<p><span>胡某红为感谢杨立平的帮助和支持，多次送给杨立平人民币共计</span><span>24</span><span>万元，杨立平均予以收受。</span></p>
<p><span><strong>过去三年违法违规两次</strong></span></p>
<p><span>2019</span><span>年，艾隆科技及子公司因违法违规行为两次受到行政处罚。</span></p>
<p><span>2019</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月，艾隆科技因部分疏散指示标志故障、消防水带漏水、</span><span>1</span><span>号防火门故障、</span><span>2</span><span>号卷帘门下堆放杂物、排烟设施联动未启动；占用消防车道；火灾自动报警系统存在故障、消防设施未保持完好有效等原因，收到苏州市消防救援支队工业园区大队出具的《行政处罚决定书》，合计罚款</span><span>2.6</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>2019</span><span>年</span><span>11</span><span>月，艾隆科技子公司广州艾隆收到国家税务总局广州市税务局第三稽查局出具的《税务处理决定书》（穗税三稽处【</span><span>2019</span><span>】</span><span>150642</span><span>号，因广州艾隆</span><span>2016</span><span>年的采购业务，于</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月取得了对方开具的增值税发票，并进行了认证抵扣。相关发票在</span><span>2019</span><span>年被税务部门认定为不合规发票，要求广州艾隆补税</span><span>90540.38</span><span>元、滞纳金</span><span>28854.32</span><span>元。艾隆科技称，该处理决定不构成行政处罚，亦非由广州艾隆主观故意造成。</span></p>
<p><strong><span>四年分红</span><span>5640</span><span>万元</span></strong></p>
<p><span>招股说明书显示，艾隆科技于</span><span>2017</span><span>年至</span><span>2020</span><span>年四年时间内分红三次，累计分红金额</span><span>5640</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>根据艾隆科技</span><span>2017</span><span>年</span><span>6</span><span>月</span><span>30</span><span>日召开的</span><span>2016</span><span>年年度股东大会决议，艾隆科技决定分配股利</span><span>1297.50</span><span>万元；</span></p>
<p><span>根据艾隆科技</span><span>2018</span><span>年</span><span>5</span><span>月</span><span>25</span><span>日召开的</span><span>2017</span><span>年年度股东大会决议，艾隆科技决定分配股利</span><span>1447.50</span><span>万元。</span></p>
<p><span>根据艾隆科技</span><span>2020</span><span>年</span><span>4</span><span>月</span><span>29</span><span>日召开的</span><span>2019</span><span>年年度股东大会决议，艾隆科技决定分配股利</span><span>2895.00</span><span>万元。</span></p>
➜更好保护金融消费者合法权益
http://www.sohu.com/a/428851822_120702	83445
<p>当前，消费者合法权益受到侵害的现象仍不时发生，与从业机构经营管理不规范不无关系。我国金融消费者保护工作存在部门协调不够、制度不健全、规章层级较低以及覆盖不全等短板。有必要进一步完善相关法律法规，强化金融监管部门与其他部门之间的协调配合，全方位、多角度保护金融消费者权益</p>
<p>近期，两则消息引发人们的广泛关注。一是《中国人民银行金融消费者权益保护实施办法》自2020年11月1日起施行。《办法》将原规范性文件升格为部门规章，对银行、支付机构在为金融消费者提供金融产品或者服务等行为划出多条红线，使金融消费者权益保护更加有法可依。二是银保监会于10月28日发出《关于防范金融直播营销有关风险的提示》，提醒社会公众注意防范直播营销中可能隐藏的风险。</p>
<p>这两则消息都与金融消费者权益保护相关。随着金融业快速发展，金融消费者权益受到侵害的案件不时发生。数据显示，2019年央行共接到金融消费者投诉超6.3万件，同比增长86.64%；银保监部门监管直接接收办理银行业、保险业消费者投诉事项3.13万件，同比增长69%。</p>
<p>近年来，监管部门出台了多项监管措施，对金融机构产品营销和提供服务等经营行为严加规范，对侵害消费者权益的典型案例公开曝光，加大处罚力度，提高震慑力。特别是提高监管法规的层级和效力，更加凸显了对消费者权益保护的重视。</p>
<p>不过，应清醒地认识到，消费者合法权益受到侵害的现象仍不时发生，与从业机构经营管理不规范不无关系。当前，我国金融消费者保护工作存在部门协调不够、制度不健全、规章层级较低以及覆盖不全等短板。相比之前的规定，此次央行发布的《办法》提升了法律效力，内容更加完善，但其适用对象仅限于银行业机构和非银行支付机构，一些新型金融机构、类金融机构还处于监管真空地带，对消费者权益构成了潜在风险。有必要进一步完善相关法律法规，强化金融监管部门与其他部门之间的协调配合，全方位、多角度保护金融消费者权益。</p>
<p>同时，加强金融消费者教育，提高金融素养，增强风险防范意识也不可或缺。监管部门和金融机构应充分利用各种媒介，通过多种方式加大金融知识宣传力度，让广大群众全面了解存贷款、股票债券、基金理财、投资、保险、支付以及非法集资等相关知识，提高对金融产品和服务的甄别能力，准确识别金融诈骗、误导宣传等侵害消费者合法权益的行为。金融消费者也应树立科学理性的金融投资、消费观念，理性投资，防控风险。</p>
<p>与此同时，还应着力压实金融机构消费者权益保护的主体责任。金融机构要按照国家法律法规和监管要求，完善营销展业制度规范，加强员工教育和管理，压实各部门、各岗位、各业务人员责任，及时稳妥处理业务纠纷，切实履行好和担负起消费者权益保护义务。</p>
<p>更重要的是，对于侵害金融消费者合法权益的行为，监管部门必须做到“零容忍”。要从严执法，对侵权问题屡查屡犯、整改敷衍了事、整改不及时的机构，以及问题严重、社会影响极坏的案件，要从重处罚，追究相关人员责任，并及时通报。（本文来源：经济日报 作者：李凤文）</p>
➜通业科技营收滞胀去年主营收现比68% 曾更正3年财报
http://www.sohu.com/a/428851909_120702	83445
<p><strong>中国经济网编者按：</strong>创业板上市委<span>2020</span>年第<span>40</span>次审议会议将于<span>11</span>月<span>3</span>日召开，届时将审议深圳通业科技股份有限公司（简称“通业科技”）的首发上市申请。</p>
<p>通业科技拟在深交所创业板上市，保荐机构为招商证券，申报会计师为上会会计师事务所（特殊普通合伙）。本次发行数量不超过<span>2560</span>万股，占发行后总股本的<span>25.00%</span>，全部为公开发行新股，不安排公司股东公开发售股份。通业科技拟募集资金<span>3.84</span>亿元，其中，<span>1.16</span>亿元用于轨道交通电气装备扩产项目，<span>8947.10</span>万元用于维保基地及服务网点建设及升级项目，<span>5234.83</span>万元用于研发中心升级建设项目，<span>4080.24</span>万元用于信息管理系统升级建设项目，<span>8500.00</span>万元用于补充流动资金。</p>
<p>通业科技自成立以来主要从事轨道交通机车车辆电气产品的研发、生产、销售和维保服务，形成了电源产品、智能控制产品、电机及风机产品三大产品类型，初步覆盖了从电源供电、控制监控到电气终端执行部件的轨道交通机车车辆电气产品生态链，同时提供相关产品的维保服务。</p>
<p>截至招股说明书签署日，谢玮直接持有<span>3468</span>万股股份，占发行前股本总额的<span>45.1646%</span>，系通业科技的控股股东。谢玮与徐建英系夫妻关系，为共同实际控制人，直接和间接合计持有公司<span>74.16%</span>的股份。</p>
<p>据招股说明书，通业科技在<span>2017</span>年至今现金分红<span>4</span>次，合计分红金额为<span>8488.20</span>万元。</p>
<p>报告期内，通业科技资产负债率远高于同行业平均水平，而流动比率和速动比率均低于同行业平均水平。</p>
<p><span>2017</span>年末至<span>2020</span>年<span>6</span>月末，通业科技资产总额分别为<span>4.41</span>亿元、<span>5.06</span>亿元、<span>5.79</span>亿元、<span>6.02</span>亿元；负债合计<span>2.28</span>亿元、<span>2.61</span>亿元、<span>2.85</span>亿元、<span>2.81</span>亿元；公司资产负债率（合并）分别为<span>51.72%</span>、<span>51.62%</span>、<span>49.20%</span>、<span>46.70%</span>。同期，同行业上市公司资产负债率平均值分别为<span>28.02%</span>、<span>29.92%</span>、<span>25.16%</span>、<span>22.97%</span>。</p>
<p><span>2017</span>年末、<span>2018</span>年末、<span>2019</span>年末及<span>2020</span>年<span>6</span>月末，通业科技流动比率分别为<span>1.99</span>、<span>1.95</span>、<span>2.07</span>及<span>2.19</span>，速动比率分别为<span>1.56</span>、<span>1.50</span>、<span>1.66</span>及<span>1.75</span>。同期，同行业上市公司流动比率平均值分别为<span>4.42</span>、<span>3.83</span>、<span>3.99</span>、<span>5.06</span>，速动比率平均值分别为<span>3.89</span>、<span>3.25</span>、<span>3.49</span>、<span>4.44</span>。</p>
<p>报告期内，通业科技三年销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金不敌营业收入，且<span>2020</span>年营收净利预计双降。</p>
<p><span>2017</span>年、<span>2018</span>年、<span>2019</span>年和<span>2020</span>年<span>6</span>月，通业科技的营业收入分别为<span>3.12</span>亿元、<span>3.60</span>亿元、<span>3.89</span>亿元和<span>1.34</span>亿元；主营业务收入分别为<span>3.06</span>亿元、<span>3.52</span>亿元、<span>3.83</span>亿元和<span>1.31</span>亿元；销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金分别为<span>2.46</span>亿元、<span>2.87</span>亿元、<span>2.60</span>亿元、<span>1.56</span>亿元。</p>
<p>同期，通业科技净利润分别为<span>5351.12</span>万元、<span>5189.08</span>万元、<span>7421.40</span>万元、<span>2646.42</span>万元；扣除非经常性损益后归属于母公司所有者的净利润分别为<span>5087.30</span>万元、<span>6087.81</span>万元、<span>7143.73</span>万元和<span>2426.71</span>万元；经营活动产生的现金流量净额分别为<span>4997.89</span>万元、<span>5474.31</span>万元、<span>4478.35</span>万元、<span>3507.23</span>万元。</p>
<p>据中国经济网记者计算，<span>2017</span>年至<span>2020</span>年<span>6</span>月，通业科技主营业务收现比率分别为<span>0.80</span>、<span>0.82</span>、<span>0.68</span>、<span>1.19</span>；净现比（经营现金流量净额<span>/</span>净利润）分别是<span>0.93</span>、<span>1.05</span>、<span>0.60</span>、<span>1.33</span>。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
